task.summary: It compiles! This is a starting point, i suppose!
It's playable! Updated admin commands to save spawns, added saving of config on stop; added prepared statements for gun / perk / loadout insertion.
Fixed a load of bugs in pretty-much everything
Started implementing custom events and event handlers to better-manage the minigame. Began re-working the chatcommand system
Updated most/all threads / runnables- Updated fPlayer, updated loadout menus
Added automagic database creations Optimized admin commands optimized player commands
Added handlers for events called custom events instead of the methods directly
Updated custom event handler, Gun config, listeners, and weapon renders

Fixed issue with synchronization of player data when joining Created a thread-safe singleton for the menu close behaviour Cleaned up methods in the GameSetupHandler Hot-fix for nullpointerexception in ValidateMap.java due to maps not existing Reverted the open kits action to players using /kit
Cleaned up classes, removed most un-used methods, variables, and so forth
Removed Menu behaviours from menus as it's causing issues
